    <item>
      <title>比特币从 10 万美元回落，创特朗普胜选以来最差纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/bitcoin-btc-retreats-from-100-000-in-worst-spell-since-trump-s-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币创下了自唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国大选以来最长的连续下跌记录，此前比特币价格曾跌至 10 万美元以下，且美国总统当选人对加密货币的热情正在降温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/bitcoin-btc-retreats-from-100-000-in-worst-spell-since-trump-s-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 01:13:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税威胁再起，美元上涨，拖累比索兑加元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/dollar-rallies-mexican-peso-slumps-on-trump-s-tariff-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当选总统唐纳德·特朗普新的关税威胁削弱了人们对他挑选的财政部长将减轻政府贸易政策打击的押注，美元强势反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/dollar-rallies-mexican-peso-slumps-on-trump-s-tariff-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 00:09:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：特朗普关税威胁导致美元上涨、股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国候任总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，美国将对中国、墨西哥和加拿大征收额外关税，此举加剧了人们对其“美国优先”政策的担忧，随后美元上涨，亚洲股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 22:35:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称 Ken Leech 将 6 亿美元转入有利投资组合</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/ken-leech-sued-by-sec-over-alleged-cherry-picking-scheme</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乍一看，美国针对明星债券交易员肯·利奇的诉讼集中在程序上的一个怪癖：西方资产管理公司 (Western Asset Management Co.) 前联席首席投资官每天都会进行押注，然后等上几个小时才将其分配到客户的投资组合中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/ken-leech-sued-by-sec-over-alleged-cherry-picking-scheme</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 21:53:49 GMT</pubDate>
